name: Tracker

next_episode_to_air.name: Trust Fall
next_episode_to_air.overview: While searching for missing campers, Colter meets a retired police officer who believes a serial killer is on the loose.

overview: Lone-wolf survivalist Colter Shaw roams the country as a “reward seeker,” using his expert tracking skills to help private citizens and law enforcement solve all manner of mysteries while contending with his own fractured family.

episodes.name: Klamath Falls
episodes.overview: Colter investigates the disappearance of 14-year-old Gil Brown, who is suspected to have been taken by his birth dad with a criminal background, and finds himself in some trouble of his own, requiring help from legal mind Reenie Greene.

episodes.name: Missoula
episodes.overview: Colter tracks down a missing young man who has been pulled into a deadly cult and doesn't want to be found.

episodes.name: Springland
episodes.overview: As Colter helps a young woman locate her free-spirited sister, he digs deeper into how the sister's last days may lead to a dark secret she unearthed in this tight-knit town.

episodes.name: Mt. Shasta
episodes.overview: Colter races against the clock to find the missing teenage son of Reenie's close friend Erika.

episodes.name: St. Louis
episodes.overview: The odds are stacked against Colter as he is tasked by a convicted murderer's teenage daughter to track down a missing witness who could prove her dad's innocence.

episodes.name: Lexington
episodes.overview: Colter reluctantly teams up with his nemesis, fellow reward seeker Billie Matalon, to track down a missing racehorse.

episodes.name: Chicago
episodes.overview: Colter, Bobby and Reenie race against time to track down a talented MMA fighter who disappeared while trying to solve her family’s trouble with their visas.

episodes.name: Camden
episodes.overview: Colter tracks down a dockworker who went missing two weeks before his wedding following a confrontation with his past.

episodes.name: Aurora
episodes.overview: When a widower offers a reward to find his only daughter who disappeared three years ago and is presumed dead, Colter agrees to help track her down.

episodes.name: Into the Wild
episodes.overview: Colter journeys into the wilderness of Idaho to help track down the owner of an aerial outfitting company's missing adult children who were last seen in a plane that took off during bad weather with a mysterious client on board.

episodes.name: Beyond the Campus Walls
episodes.overview: When a grad student goes missing after a house party, his friends and family believe he buckled under the pressure of his research grant. But, after consulting with his sister Dr. Dory Shaw, a professor at the school, Colter uncovers a trail of explicit photos and messages that lead him to uncover a dangerous – and deadly – conspiracy on campus.

episodes.name: Off the Books
episodes.overview: Colter is forced to team up with his estranged brother, Russell, who enlists his help to track down a former army buddy who's gone missing after several weeks of paranoid behavior. The investigation takes the brothers into the world of Special Forces missions, shady off-the-books programs and conspiracy theories, all while they contend with their family's past.

episodes.name: The Storm
episodes.overview: Colter investigates the disappearance of two amateur storm chasers, one of whom is the daughter of an old family friend, that the local police have written off as an accidental drowning. Colter's expert tracking skills lead him to uncover the seedy underbelly of a small town resort.

episodes.name: Out of the Past
episodes.overview: The disappearance of a family in the backwoods of Arkansas leads Colter to a shocking discovery.

episodes.name: Ontological Shock
episodes.overview: When Colter disappears during his search for a missing father, Reenie recruits his brother Russell for help.

episodes.name: Bloodlines
episodes.overview: Colter and rival rewardist Billie Matalon team up to find a missing high school baseball star.

episodes.name: Noble Rot
episodes.overview: Reenie gets Colter to take a case involving a woman missing from a high-end wellness retreat in Napa designed for CEOs.

episodes.name: Preternatural
episodes.overview: Colter takes a job locating a missing teen with a unique spiritual gift in an inhospitable mining town.

episodes.name: Trust Fall
episodes.overview: While searching for missing campers, Colter meets a retired police officer who believes a serial killer is on the loose.
